definitions.definition: The twelfth and last month of the Gregorian calendar , following November and preceding the January of the following year, containing the southern solstice .
A female given name transferred from the month name [in turn from English] .

main_definition: The twelfth and last month of the Gregorian calendar , following November and preceding the January of the following year, containing the southern solstice .
